snippet.title: Pluto Lost Its Colors! [Gameplay Trailer]
snippet.description:
Introducing the latest platformer video game by NINES - Pluto Lost Its Colors!

Join Pluto in its quest to reclaim its colors! 

Pluto's peaceful existence was disturbed when it was attacked by a menacing Black Hole, losing its colors in the ensuing battle.
Help Pluto reclaim its color by collecting color shards spread across the galaxy.

Available now to wishlist on Steam and Epic Games.

https://pluto.ninesconnect.com

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2935260/Pluto_Lost_Its_Colors/
https://store.epicgames.com/p/pluto-lost-its-colors-4fb4c4
